OL,5, A Utah woman who published a children's
OL,6, book about grief after the sudden death
OL,7, of her husband has been charged with   
OL,8, his murder.                            
OL,10,FKouri Richins, a mother of three,      
OL,11,Fcalled police late one night in March  
OL,12,F2022 and said her husband, Eric        
OL,13,FRichins, was "cold to the touch".      
OL,15,FShe told authorities she had made her  
OL,16,Fhusband a mixed vodka drink before     
OL,17,Ffinding him unresponsive hours later.  
OL,19,FA medical examiner later found Mr      
OL,20,FRichins died from a fentanyl overdose. 
